{
  "stem": "1704.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in the beginning, the first month, nothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everything went as normal.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But then gradually, I had to register.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had to wear the star.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were not allowed in the trains, in the buses, not allowed in certain shops.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were shops only for Jews, and shops no Jews allowed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Not in parks, not travelling.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You had to get a special pass if you wanted to travel.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In by 8 o'clock at night, like a curfew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And, you know, it became worse and worse.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, but I woke up in the morning and grandmother-- the Germans have invaded.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You have to be careful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now we can't talk.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you have to be very careful and, and the bombardment of Rotterdam you heard on the radio.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was very bad in Rotterdam.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, not-- me, not personal.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because, you know, as I said, I never paid much attention.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I think my parents did.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] May, 1940.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I then said to my father, look.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Lots of people trying to get to England.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why don't we [INAUDIBLE]?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's not none of your business.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Keep out of it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's what the answer, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was not up to the children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were seen-- to be seen and not heard.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Father knows best, and he didn't.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, because there was not much opportunity.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was only a few days, and then, you know, after they invaded, and Holland capitulated, it was finished.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you couldn't get out then anyway.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, and there was nothing we could flee to because, you know, the border was Germany.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Belgium was also occupied.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All we could do was [INAUDIBLE] to see, through the worst.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when you actually had to wear the stars--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they had a big strike.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody stopped work.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
